How to File? Use the LRDR codes to determine how borrowers are counted for the cohort year. Submit the IDC if the data you have reported to NSLDS contradicts the information on the LRDR. Ensure that you have the borrower’s SSN, name, basis of alleged error and copies of relevant supporting documentation.
